pens new\npossibilities for attacking a broad class of phenomena governed by the coupling\nof geometry and mechanics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Sep 2018 20:22:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Jan 2019 20:59:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-08"}
