the neural network execution time by $48\\%$ to\n$78\\%$ and energy consumption by $37\\%$ to $69\\%$ compared with the\nstate-of-the-art compression algorithms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Sep 2018 00:43:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-20"}
