 the insufficient data precision, or as\nthe overestimation of $(H_0, \\Omega_m)$ values -- we discuss both\npossibilities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Sep 2018 12:18:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Sep 2018 14:38:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-24"}
