ve tensors of such systems on the wave\nvector is not removable even at very small frequencies and incidence angles and\nthat analytical considerations significantly limit the potential forms of the\nspatially dispersive constitutive tensors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Sep 2018 15:02:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-20"}
